  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-03-08",
    "date": "2022-03-18T20:58:54Z",
    "text": "Financing Lead Out of Water Act of 2022\n\nThis bill allows the issuance of tax-exempt private activity bonds to finance the replacement of any privately-owned portion of a lead service line in a public water system. Specifically, the bill provides that the use of proceeds from such bonds for replacement of a lead service line does not constitute private business use."
